posts.body:
Gogo Racing Patch Notes

1.0.1 Patch Note

‚ö° Revision was made on Product category, so expired products can't be install anymore.

‚ö° After purchasing fixed-term items, the expiration display has been modified to be displayed when the expiration date expires.

‚ö° [Game Mode] It has been modified so that the sound is output when the back button is touched.

‚ö° [Garage] The vehicle name display length has been modified.

‚ö° Revised to remove expired characters and vehicles when updating inventory.

‚ö° Fixed the alignment of the character above the in-game and the name display that were misplaced.

‚ö° Added Tapjoy Shop Event icon and function.

‚ö° Fixed an issue where store alignment did not work properly.

‚ö° Modified the profile to expose character vehicle stats and skill information.

‚ö° [Garage] We modified the items that is currently installing so that they are aligned at the front.

‚ö° [Garage] If Players have more than one same paint, we have improved it to indicate the quantity on one item.

‚ö° [Option] We adjusted the size of the web view window considering the sizes of the device.

‚ö° [Option] Fix related to web view back Button issue

       ‚û°Ô∏è Add store data

       ‚û°Ô∏è Disable the Login Guest button

posts.title: üîä 1.0.3 Patch Note
posts.body:
Gogo Racing Patch Notes

1.0.3 Patch Note

Fix version informations:

‚ö° Fixed incorrect game information version.

‚ö° Modified game reward icon to appear differently when you lose the game.

‚ö° Fixed vehicle change pop-up error in the matching room.

‚ö° Added exception if the expired characters are installed.

‚ö° Revised exception handling if the expired vehicle is installed.

‚ö° Fixed sound setting: to prevent sound from coming out when the effect was turned off.

‚ö° Fixed / Adjusted reward icon size.

‚ö° Applied correction on the item acquisition effect when using magnetic field items.

‚ö° Applied correction on turtle attack whereas the attack effect does not disappear when the shield is used.

‚ö° Fixed Attendance Reward Pop-up.

‚ö° Languages:

‚ö° Added 7 new text translations: Japanese, Indonesian, Vietnamese, Thai, Spanish, French, and Italian.

‚ö° Unavailable language is locked for processing.

‚ö° Fixed issue where language is set automatically when the user moved to the lobby

 33. Fixed skid marks not being displayed properly.

 34. Fixed parts that were not translated in the GrandPrix.

 35. Fixed the part where the scaffold animation was not working.

 36. Translated English display for characters, maps, and vehicles.

 37. Fixed to display "Complete" instead of "Receive" when completing a quest.

gameguide.title: üí≥ Purchase & Linking Guide
gameguide.gdescription: This will guide you on how to purchase items in GoGo Racing using different types of payment method.
gameguide.body:
Selecting a payment method

The game will ask you to select your preferred payment method in order to successfully purchase into the game.

Types of payment methods:

GCash

üåü Select GCash as your payment method and tap ‚ÄúContinue‚Äù.

üåü Enter your GCash MPIN if you have any.

üåü Check the checkbox for GCash Terms and Conditions and tap ‚ÄúAuthorize‚Äù.

üåü An authentication code will be sent to your GCash. Input the code and tap ‚ÄúNext‚Äù.

üåü When linking is successful. Press ‚ÄúOKAY‚Äù.

üåü When GCash is selected as a payment method, press ‚ÄúBuy‚Äù to proceed on purchasing.

Debit/Credit Card

üåü Input your Debit/Credit Card number.

Input your other Credit/Debit card details

üåü Once done, tap ‚ÄúSave‚Äù.

üåü When Debit/Credit card is selected as a payment method, press ‚ÄúBuy‚Äù to proceed on purchasing.

Paypal

üåü Input your PayPal email address.

üåü Input your PayPal phone number.

üåü Verify your PayPal account using by requesting a code by tapping ‚ÄúRequest Code‚Äù.

üåü A security code will be sent to your PayPal number to input it to the text box and tap ‚ÄúVerify‚Äù.

üåü When PayPal is selected as a payment method, press ‚ÄúBuy‚Äù to proceed on purchasing.
